WORKDIR /app

COPY . .

RUN dotnet publish -c Release -o /out

FROM mcr.microsoft.com/dotnet/aspnet:8.0

WORKDIR /app

COPY --from=build /out .

ENTRYPOINT ["dotnet", "ExcelService.dll"]
No Office installation required in the image. No special fonts or system libraries required. This Dockerfile works for both NPOI and IronXL projects, and it follows Docker multi-stage build best practices.|  |  |  |
